posts.label: Research
posts.title: Research at University of Illinois Urbana Champaign
posts.__html:
• Working in Social Spaces Group with Karrie Karahalios, Kristen Vaccaro and other fellow undergraduate students
  • Refactored a web app that allows users to connect to social media API and filter their new feed to get a sense of how algorithms and filters affect their feeds.
  • Exploratory data mining, predictive machine learning and analysis on recidivism data scraped from government websites and apis, including developing visualizations and regression models.
